makers (WHO, 2010). Available from http://www.who.int/health_financing/pb_e_10_01-ghana-
nhis.pdf. 
</p>
<p> 8 Catriona Waddington and K.E. Enyimayew, &#8220;A price to pay: The impact of user charges in Ashanti-
