(1989), pp. 17-47. 
</p>
<p> 9 M. Aikins, S. J. Anie, P. Apoya, S. Grey, <i>A survey of health financing schemes in Ghana</i> (Dakar, 
PHRplus, 2001). 
</p>
<p> 10 Oxfam International, <i>Achieving a Shared Goal:  Free Universal Health Care in Ghana</i> (March 2011), 
